{
  "title": "ICU-SLEEP — Investigation of Sleep in the Intensive Care Unit (analysis code)",
  "description": "Analysis pipeline for the ICU-SLEEP randomized controlled trial of nocturnal dexmedetomidine (Dex) in non-ventilated medical/surgical ICU patients aged 50+ (NCT03355053; MGB IRB #2017P000090). Reproduces baseline characteristic tables, primary and secondary outcomes (in-hospital and ICU delirium-free days), 3-arm sensitivity analyses, survival/mortality, and forest plots. Companion data is distributed via bdsp.io and AWS S3 (s3://bdsp-opendata-credentialed/icu-sleep/).",
  "license": "MIT",
